| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3236 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 901cd981-99d4-585e-8eb5-501c52352dbe"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
